text: Kückelheim is a locality in the municipality Schmallenberg in the district Hochsauerlandkreis in North Rhine-Westphalia, Germany. The village has 80 inhabitantsSchmallenberg.de: Inhabitants and lies in the west of the municipality of Schmallenberg at a height of around 390 m. Kückelheim borders on the villages of Arpe, Bracht, Selkentrop and Werntrop. ==References== Category:Villages in North Rhine-Westphalia Category:Schmallenberg
